For Suricata

Two NICs same VLAN
Requires a VIP on the fw in the source VLAN 

auto lo
iface lo inet loopback

auto eth0
iface eth0 inet static
    address 10.10.0.1
    netmask 255.255.255.0
    gateway 10.10.0.254

auto eth1
iface eth1 inet static
    address 10.10.0.2
    netmask 255.255.255.0
    up ip route add 10.10.0.11/32 dev eth1
    up ip route add 10.10.0.5/32 dev eth1
    up ip route add 10.10.0.141/32 dev eth1
    up ip route add 10.10.0.21/32 dev eth1
